> > > This patch makes sk_alloc GFP_ATOMIC, because we are holding the bt_proto_rwlock, for
> > > the following functions:
> > > - bnep_sock_create
> > > - cmtp_sock_create
> > > - hci_sock_create
> > > - hidp_sock_create
> > > - l2cap_sock_create
